                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d679">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">McCormick</persName> to Mr.
                            <persName type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Embassy</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">St. Petersburg</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1904-02-08">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 8, 1904</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. McCormick reports that he has been informed by the minister for foreign
                    affairs that the Russian minister at Tokyo had the Russian reply when the
                    Japanese minister asked for his passports.)</p>
            </div>
